#

Vegetarian Borshch

75 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A hearty and vibrant beetroot soup full of vegetables, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beetroot: 3 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrot: 1 large, diced
  • potato: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • sugar: 1 teaspoon
